# List of useful programs for CTFs

# Forensics
xxd                                                                     # hex dump of a file
stegsolve                                                               # allows you to apply different filters over images
Wireshark                                                               # traffic analyzer

# Web App
sqlmap                                                                  # automate SQLi
Burpsuite                                                               # intercept connection, look at requests and responses, fuzzing
nmap                                                                    # helpful all around networking tool
netcat                                                                  # simple networking from command line
Web Scarab                                                              # alternative to Burpsuite

# Binary Exploitation
Radare2                                                                 # reverse engineering framework
gdb                                                                     # debugger
IDA                                                                     # reverse engineering and disassembling
